original_title: This Ain't Star Trek XXX 2: The Butterfly Effect
overview: Kirk, Spock & Bones beam down to Butterfly 8 where they are ambushed by female aliens. When Scotty beams Sulu and Chekov down to rescue them, a transporter malfunction sends them to the Oval office the day before Kennedy was shot.
title: This Ain't Star Trek XXX 2: The Butterfly Effect
